ORO.MLR.100 (a)    The emergency equipment was  inspected before the flight and found to be in proper working condition. However, the location of the PBE and Portable oxygen bottles is not compliant with the Aircraft Emergency Safety Equipment Manual, Part A 319/320/320N. Please provide the correct information of this emergency equipment according to the correct location.
